Remove boost from BPAD/EMBER farm.

&nbsp; 

 Economic impact

BPAD farm will get less APR.

&nbsp; 

Impact on users

The boost will move automatically to flexUSD/EMBER so they will see better APR on that farm.

&nbsp; 

Expected impact

Less liquidity on BPAD, more liquidity on flexUSD if any changes happen.

&nbsp; 

Expected positive impact

Better flexUSD APR, less selling pressure on EMBER from BPAD farm.
